    "The speed of pressure change and speed of pressure change frequencies are the other derivable features from pressure values.",
    "The tilt feature is used to measure the inclination of the pen or pencil used for writing.",
    "The azimuth angle of a pen or pencil with respect to the plane of the written surface is also quantified for feature set construction.",
    "Tilt and azimuth angle are displayed in Fig. 8.",
    "• Other FeaturesApart from the main four categories of features (Kinematic, temporal, spatial, dynamic), few works in the literature have considered some other features to improve the dysgraphia screening efficiency."
